@startuml red-green-refactor

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Red-Green-Refactor Cycle

state "🔴 RED\nWrite a failing test" as red #FFcccc
state "✅ GREEN\nMake it pass\n(simplest code)" as green #ccFFcc
state "♻️ REFACTOR\nImprove design\n(tests protect you)" as refactor #ccccFF

[*] --> red
red --> green : implement
green --> refactor : clean up
refactor --> red : next test
refactor --> [*] : done

note right of red
  Test must fail.
  If it passes, something
  is wrong with the test.
end note

note right of green
  Write the minimum code.
  Fake It if unsure.
end note

note right of refactor
  Eliminate duplication.
  Improve names.
  Run tests after each change.
end note

@enduml
